0 0 700 525 re
f
GR
GS
[0.48 0 0 0.48018 0 62.90397] CT
[1 0 0 1 0 0] CT
N
0 -131 M
875 -131 L
875 525 L
0 525 L
0 -131 L
cp
clip
GS
0 0 translate
700 525 scale
